---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Notes">
  <section class="content-card">
    <p class="eyebrow">Notes</p>
    <h1 class="page-title">Notes Archive</h1>
    <p>Long-form notes are not yet part of the Astro migration.</p>
    <p>
      If this section matters, the next step is to model notes as Markdown or MDX content under
      <code>src/content</code> or <code>src/pages</code>.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
